{"tid":19480,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"求一個正常sound bar","createTime":"2016-12-02T20:28:49.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T16:00:11.000Z","uid":48405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9406a454eaf9b15d7204018706a7cc1338b5bc90","tid":19480,"uid":48405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T20:28:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/042412_abf239b4e000a866b5f39ff081f21e13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F042412_abf239b4e000a866b5f39ff081f21e13.jpg&h=55b8c2d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想要類似呢種 因為書枱唔大 唔想一舊兩舊喇叭咁肉酸 想一條過 又美觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係聽人講razer呢隻好垃圾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無啲2000蚊樓下性價比比較高？<br />\n我唔係好好好著重音效 外型睇重啲 我木耳黎 當然聲音要正常啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec30df6211cb05a5f427acf76eaea31de956d00f","tid":19480,"uid":48405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T20:29:38.000Z","msg":"應該要叫 求一個靚仔sound bar"},{"pid":"b5512c772c70bbf84fe76e0dab4872d991b19ede","tid":19480,"uid":1818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T20:33:37.000Z","msg":"睇重外型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人唔笑狗都吠"},{"pid":"bdf39874678adffbf1ac98ae6888729e07acaead","tid":19480,"uid":12902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T20:35:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/043515_53de478da5a3a4ac802df9db2de31ad4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F043515_53de478da5a3a4ac802df9db2de31ad4.jpg&h=c2d15036&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"909bffed736f7a8ca6308dcbd0039879c6e53b34","tid":19480,"uid":48405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T20:44:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇重外型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人唔笑狗都吠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實有時你放得啲嘢係枱面 都係想靚靚仔仔 乾乾淨淨姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能我地用途唔同姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"588447c34324688d8edbbd93e979e1bdb6e17033","tid":19480,"uid":1149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T20:45:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/042412_abf239b4e000a866b5f39ff081f21e13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F042412_abf239b4e000a866b5f39ff081f21e13.jpg&h=55b8c2d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想要類似呢種 因為書枱唔大 唔想一舊兩舊喇叭咁肉酸 想一條過 又美觀[img]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/img] <br />\n但係聽人講razer呢隻好垃圾 [img]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/img] 有無啲2000蚊樓下性價比比較高？<br />\n我唔係好好好著重音效 外型睇重啲 我木耳黎 當然聲音要正常啦[img]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/img] [img]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/img] [img]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/img] [img]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/img] [img]<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/img]</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"584f5f14b08a26100d643b8fe88fb1bfb9156ae5","tid":19480,"uid":48405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T20:46:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/043515_53de478da5a3a4ac802df9db2de31ad4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F043515_53de478da5a3a4ac802df9db2de31ad4.jpg&h=c2d15036&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個有睇過 好吸引 但係如果佢有扁啲矮啲就好<br />\nThankyou清"},{"pid":"91d6bf5093fff1ec0737119cd44496eb41575972","tid":19480,"uid":266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T22:41:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/03/064142_d8096849ff0c03ed5d394bda9ba8b464.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F03%2F064142_d8096849ff0c03ed5d394bda9ba8b464.jpg&h=a084c7b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4d995e5f42b49e3fb734de5a679b9905520beeb","tid":19480,"uid":17324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T23:38:17.000Z","msg":"用緊Bose Soundlink mini 2<br />\nd 聲靚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   同級暫時都重係無對手"},{"pid":"e032816231e9daf8cc846b6edbc0c7fffd27f24f","tid":19480,"uid":48405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T05:28:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用緊Bose Soundlink mini 2<br />\nd 聲靚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   同級暫時都重係無對手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似幾正 但唔係for電腦？razer個隻啲聲係咪真係差到仆街"},{"pid":"ff9145bd15927a7cb193e2536ff74474295f2ee5","tid":19480,"uid":15471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T15:41:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用緊Bose Soundlink mini 2<br />\nd 聲靚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   同級暫時都重係無對手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似幾正 但唔係for電腦？razer個隻啲聲係咪真係差到仆街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n落黃金自己試啦屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你想揾細隻soundbar其實都無乜選擇"},{"pid":"8493d47699cdd2e344da5e02573ece1340930d16","tid":19480,"uid":20948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T16:00:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用緊Bose Soundlink mini 2<br />\nd 聲靚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   同級暫時都重係無對手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好似幾正 但唔係for電腦？razer個隻啲聲係咪真係差到仆街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n用左幾個月，感覺幾好，有埋subwoofer打機都幾正<br />\n幾個mode唔同EQ setting，有得玩fiber同藍芽<br />\n不過間房格局做唔到佢聲稱個5.1<br />\n<br />\n相同價位實有靚聲好多既2.1，有subwoofer既sound bar就未必有，但個人仍然覺得抵玩<br />\n<br />\nbetween上網搵下啲promotion code/學生優惠之類，可能平啲<br />\n<br />\n利申：有獨立聲卡+用fiber，官網買"}]}